{"title":"Berd Peregrine Aero Wheels – Speed Meets Vibration Damping","link":"https://bikerumor.com/berd-peregrine-aero-wheels-speed-meets-vibration-damping/","date":1739286326000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-rim-62V.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"428\" alt=\"Berd Peregrine Aero wheels rim 62V\" /></p>\n<p>Berd has teamed up with the aero gurus at HED Cycling to create the <strong>Peregrine Aero Wheels</strong>—a blend of ultralight, flex-tuned Berd spokes and HED’s wind-cheating rim tech. The new Peregrine wheels center around the <strong>HED Vanquish V62</strong> rims <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/hed-vanquish-aero-road-wheels-get-wider-faster/\">(read our entire tech piece here</a>). And yes, like a proper Midwest collaboration, they’re handcrafted in Minnesota.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-header.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1646\" height=\"1082\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-header.png\" alt=\"Berd Peregrine Aero wheels\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-header.png 1646w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-header-297x195.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-header-1536x1010.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-header-120x79.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-header-768x505.png 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(All images: Berd Spokes) </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Lightest Spokes in the Game</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Berd’s <strong>Polylight Spokes</strong> are the lightest in the world. That’s not marketing fluff—that’s a fact. These spokes don’t just shave grams; their natural vibration-damping properties take the edge off harsh road feedback, making for a ride that’s smooth, lively, and easy on the body. Paired with the stiff, aero profile of the V62 rims, you’re looking at a balance of efficiency and comfort that’s hard to beat.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-hubs-.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"399\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-hubs-.png\" alt=\"Berd Peregrine Aero wheels hubs\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-hubs-.png 640w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-hubs--297x185.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-hubs--120x75.png 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Built Around the Berd Talon Hubs</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Holding it all together is the Berd Talon hubset, purpose-built for Berd’s unique spokes. Weighing in at just 359 grams per set, these hubs bring elite-level durability and performance in a lightweight package. Choose from 11/12 Speed, Microspline, or XDR driver options.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-I9-hubs.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"393\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-I9-hubs.png\" alt=\"Berd Peregrine Aero wheels I9 hubs\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-I9-hubs.png 640w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-I9-hubs-297x182.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-I9-hubs-120x74.png 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Looking to Drop Even More Grams?</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Industry Nine Solix option trims even more weight for the gram-counters while still delivering that signature snappy engagement. Available with XDR, HG 11/12-Speed, Microspline, or Campy N3W driver bodies.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-HED-.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1842\" height=\"1082\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-HED-.png\" alt=\"Berd Peregrine Aero wheels HED\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-HED-.png 1842w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-HED--297x174.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-HED--1536x902.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-HED--120x70.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-HED--768x451.png 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>How much lighter are the Peregrine wheels vs the HED Vanquish V62 Pro series? </em>HED quotes the V62 Pro series wheelset at  1673g ± 30g. That includes a build with Sapim CX-ray, hooked spokes, and a HED branded hubset. The Berd Peregrine wheels are quoted at 1,534g without tape or valves…</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-rim-62V.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-rim-62V.png\" alt=\"Berd Peregrine Aero wheels rim 62V\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-rim-62V.png 640w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-rim-62V-297x199.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-rim-62V-120x80.png 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Fully Minnesota-Made Edition</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Want to keep it 100% USA-made? </em>The Onyx Vesper Hook Flange build is as homegrown as it gets. Every piece—Berd spokes, Onyx hubs, and HED rims—is created and assembled within a 60-mile radius in Minnesota. If supporting local craftsmanship is high on your priority list, this one’s for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"188\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-.png\" alt=\"Berd Peregrine Aero wheels\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-.png 640w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels--297x87.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels--120x35.png 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Pricing, Availability</strong> &amp; Specs</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Berd Talon Hubs</strong> – $2,495</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Industry Nine Solix Hubs</strong> – $2,595</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Onyx Vesper Hook Flange Hubs</strong> – $2,695</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-weight-.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"357\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-weight-.png\" alt=\"Berd Peregrine Aero wheels weight\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-weight-.png 640w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-weight--297x166.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Berd-Peregrine-Aero-wheels-weight--120x67.png 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Limited stock is available.<a href=\"https://berdspokes.com/\"> Berdspokes.com</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/berd-peregrine-aero-wheels-speed-meets-vibration-damping/\">Berd Peregrine Aero Wheels – Speed Meets Vibration Damping</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"9d97e169a64e1a716c64b4bed1a1833497d6899426ef2e775fbd3c5e59420fb4","category":"Cycling"}